                        <p>Lunes a viernes de 14:00 a 18:00 hrs.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="w-full lg:w-1/2 lg:p-4">
                        <figure><img src="https://contenido.oyedigital.mx/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/DIEGO-oye.png" alt=""></figure>
